   "source": [
    "# Lead Origin\n",
    "a = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Lead Origin'], prefix = 'Lead Origin', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final0 = pd.concat([dataset,a], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Lead Source\n",
    "b = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Lead Source'], prefix = 'Lead Source', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final1 = pd.concat([dataset_final0, b], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Last Activity\n",
    "c = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Last Activity'], prefix = 'Last Activity', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final2 = pd.concat([dataset_final1, c], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Country\n",
    "d = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Country'], prefix = 'Country', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final3 = pd.concat([dataset_final2, d], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Specialization\n",
    "e = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Specialization'], prefix = 'Specialization', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final4 = pd.concat([dataset_final3, d], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "#What is your current occupation\n",
    "f = pd.get_dummies(dataset['What is your current occupation'], prefix = 'What is your current occupation', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final5 = pd.concat([dataset_final4, f], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# What matters most to you in choosing a course\n",
    "g = pd.get_dummies(dataset['What matters most to you in choosing a course'], prefix = 'What matters most to you in choosing a course', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final6 = pd.concat([dataset_final5, g], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tags\n",
    "h = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Tags'], prefix = 'Tags', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final7 = pd.concat([dataset_final6, h], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# City\n",
    "i = pd.get_dummies(dataset['City'], prefix = 'City', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final8 = pd.concat([dataset_final7,i], axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Last Notable Activity\n",
    "j = pd.get_dummies(dataset['Last Notable Activity'], prefix = 'Last Notable Activity', drop_first = True, dtype = int)\n",
    "dataset_final = pd.concat([dataset_final8,i], axis = 1)"
   ]

   ]

  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "id": "e35a48e4-4223-4779-afb9-d10b57fd9d94",

   "source": [
    "def draw_roc(actual, probs):\n",
    "    fpr,tpr,thresholds = metrics.roc_curve(actual, probs,drop_intermediate= False)\n",
    "    auc_score = metrics.roc_auc_score(actual, probs)\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=[5,5])\n",
    "    plt.plot(fpr,tpr,label = 'Roc curve (area = %0.2f)' % auc_score)\n",
    "    plt.plot([0,1],[0,1],'k--')\n",
    "    plt.xlim([0.0,1.0])\n",
    "    plt.ylim([0.0,1.05])\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('Flase positive rate or [1 - True Negative rate]')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('True Positive rate')\n",
    "    plt.title('Receiver operating characteristic example')\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc = \"lower right\")\n",
    "    plt.savefig('ROC.JPG')\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    return None"
   ]
  },
